{"tid":477032,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"有冇人唔開心唔會同任何人講","createTime":"2017-11-22T14:47:34.000Z","updateTime":"2018-01-21T16:57:30.000Z","uid":40746,"like":37,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":23,"replies":[{"pid":"d9d185b89d2f631de090cc8b7b24a6b6c521f7cc","tid":477032,"uid":40746,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-22T14:47:34.000Z","msg":"講完又覺得人地唔會明<br />\n有人話同人傾下 講出黎舒服啲<br />\n但講真有咩人想聽你喺度放負<br />\n試過同個朋友傾 點知事後知道原來佢覺得我煩<br />\n自此之後就冇再同人講過自己唔開心<br />\n你煩你唔開心之際 人地都有人地唔開心 煩嘅嘢<br />\n又唔想煩到其他人<br />\n<br />\n平時就成日講笑氹人地開心<br />\n人地唔開心就安慰佢地<br />\n但永遠自己唔開心嘅時候就自己喊 自己排解<br />\n而家頂唔順 唯有上黎叫下春 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"633e42f0c9b962e98d7c213f81869f19fd2c26cc","tid":477032,"uid":28748,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-22T14:51:29.000Z","msg":"有"},{"pid":"9ba87b0e8e038c93d535630fe38579fa41238eaa","tid":477032,"uid":14378,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-22T14:53:38.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"32623c24f9849b519cae5778b1db377b181bf94f","tid":477032,"uid":40746,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-22T14:56:28.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n唔開心會做啲咩"},{"pid":"10b4d9645150fe5a19222fa7d9bbd07729222cfe","tid":477032,"uid":136637,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-22T15:07:09.000Z","msg":"以前會乜柒都講出黎 而家就好似你咁"},{"pid":"371f905edf2ba2252e5ec62c3fed08d8dc9a2d7a","tid":477032,"uid":40746,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-22T15:14:39.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>以前會乜柒都講出黎 而家就好似你咁</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n好無助"},{"pid":"4e579b399ed8b95ce9936272b006799b65dc2fac","tid":477032,"uid":86125,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-22T15:16:11.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"7c64ab11ee69c808451d1cbb94c5e24bf2ebddf2","tid":477032,"uid":29093,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-22T15:20:43.000Z","msg":"不開心 就不開心 你別勉強的慰問"},{"pid":"391112fceac4081a2fc0cc131514475fe7692579","tid":477032,"uid":41315,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-22T15:21:30.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>以前會乜柒都講出黎 而家就好似你咁</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n好無助</blockquote><br />\n講都要揀人黎講架師傅<br />\n<br />\n就好似有人鍾意睇日本動漫<br />\n有人鍾意睇 tvb<br />\n有人鍾意睇美劇<br />\n<br />\n你對住個睇美劇既講tvb<br />\n你對住個睇睇 tvb 既講動漫<br />\n咁咪錯囉<br />\n<br />\n人人有唔同專長唔同喜好<br />\n唔係個個人都鍾意聽人講心事安慰人<br />\n唔係個個人都鍾意俾意見你聽你呻<br />\n<br />\n唔係熟唔熟既問題<br />\n而係喜好性格問題<br />\n你同個唔識字既嫲嫲討論美劇, 蛇都死啦"},{"pid":"4c73fcd563d2b48e2d5deac5baedcf50c6a3c0a3","tid":477032,"uid":49859,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-22T15:22:26.000Z","msg":"有咩好講，最後都係靠自己沉澱"},{"pid":"e02fb4a663457d109eab0d0678b8e3b20eb1a6ee","tid":477032,"uid":135645,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-22T15:22:49.000Z","msg":"I know that feel<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3ba4a5590730a34d8ff3023644c71ba1ed25a6a2","tid":477032,"uid":30751,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-22T15:22:53.000Z","msg":"唔鐘意同人分享<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"45dd917b358e4bdf4af464f918deea10e23dccd1","tid":477032,"uid":77948,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-22T15:23:23.000Z","msg":"岩先好嬲 之後落街吹左陣風踢完地下 返屋企了"},{"pid":"9dea77feb4e253ef932f0387d01d9e9084660014","tid":477032,"uid":40746,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-22T15:31:53.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>不開心 就不開心 你別勉強的慰問</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a366a141865409f90388128aef8aa90bdfaddffd","tid":477032,"uid":40746,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-22T15:32:48.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>岩先好嬲 之後落街吹左陣風踢完地下 返屋企了</b